This year's edition of the Chefs Delights Awards Kenya was held at the KICC, Nairobi on Friday evening. The event with Go Places Kenya, is an ongoing awards program that awards restaurants and chefs of fine fining establishments in Kenya and rewards the restaurant enthusiasts through initiative of vote and win.Sarova Hotels, Villa Rosa Kempinski, Tamarind Group and Seven Seafood and Grill were some of the big winners for best overall hotel, best Pan-Asian hotel, best restaurant group and best individual chef overall winner respectively. Guests got to enjoy 25 different cuisines, cocktails, entertainment and a VVIP red carpet experience.